\c 24
\nb
\v 1 Ngensuku zakhe uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni wenyuka\x + 2 Lan. 36.6. Dan. 1.1.\x*, njalo uJehoyakhimi waba yisikhonzi sakhe iminyaka emithathu; wasephenduka wamvukela\x + Jer. 25.1.\x*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasithuma ukumelana laye\x + Jer. 25.9. 32.28. Hez. 19.8.\x* amaviyo amaKhaladiya\x + 25.4. Jer. 35.11.\x* lamaviyo amaSiriya\x + 6.23.\x*\x + 25.4. Jer. 35.11.\x* lamaviyo amaMowabi\x + 13.20.\x*\x + 6.23.\x* lamaviyo abantwana bakoAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*, yasiwathuma ukumelana loJuda ukumchitha, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma ngesandla sezinceku zayo abaprofethi\x + 20.17. 21,12,13,14. 23.27.\x*.
\v 3 Sibili ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* \add lokho\add* kwehlela koJuda ukubasusa ebusweni bayo ngenxa yezono zikaManase\x + 21.11.\x*, njengakho konke akwenzayo,
\v 4 njalo la\add nge\add*gazi elingelacala alichithayo; ngoba wagcwalisa iJerusalema ngegazi elingelacala, iN\nd kosi\nd* engavumanga ukulithethelela\x + 21.16.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehoyakhimi, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda?
\v 6 UJehoyakhimi waselala laboyise. UJehoyakhini indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 7 Inkosi yeGibhithe kayisaphindanga futhi ukuphuma elizweni layo, ngoba inkosi yeBhabhiloni yayithethe kusukela emfuleni weGibhithe kusiya emfuleni iYufrathi, konke okwakungokwenkosi yeGibhithe.
\s UJehoyakhini labeJerusalema bathunjelwa eBhabhiloni
\p
\v 8 UJehoyakhini wayeleminyaka elitshumi lesificaminwembili lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa inyanga ezintathu eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguNehushita indodakazi kaElinathani weJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 36.9.\x*.
\v 9 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwenza konke kukayise\x + 24.19. 23.37.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ngalesosikhathi izinceku zikaNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni zenyukela eJerusalema, umuzi wasungena ekuvinjezelweni.
\v 11 UNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni wasefika wamelana lomuzi, izinceku zakhe zisawuvimbezela.
\v 12 UJehoyakhini inkosi yakoJuda wasephuma waya enkosini yeBhabhiloni\x + Jer. 24.1. 29.1,2. Hez. 17.12. 2 Lan. 36.10.\x*, yena lonina lenceku zakhe lenduna zakhe labathenwa bakhe. Inkosi yeBhabhiloni yasimthatha ngomnyaka wesificaminwembili wokubusa kwakhe.
\v 13 Yasikhupha lapho wonke amagugu endlu kaJehova lamagugu endlu yenkosi\x + 20.17.\x*; yaquma zonke izitsha zegolide\x + 16.17. 2 Lan. 36.7. Ezra 1.7. Dan. 1.2. 5.2,3.\x* uSolomoni inkosi yakoIsrayeli ayezenzile ethempelini likaJehova\x + 1 Kho. 7.48-50.\x*, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Jer. 20.5.\x*.
\v 14 Yasithumba iJerusalema yonke, leziphathamandla zonke, lawo wonke amaqhawe alamandla\x + Jer. 24.1.\x*, abathunjwa abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi\x + 24.16. Jer. 52.28.\x*, lazo zonke ingcitshi zemisebenzi labakhandi\x + 24.16. Jer. 24.1. 29.2. 1 Sam. 13.19,22.\x*; kakusalanga loyedwa ngaphandle kwabantukazana ebantwini belizwe\x + 25.12.\x*.
\v 15 Yasimthumbela uJehoyakhini eBhabhiloni\x + 2 Lan. 36.10. Esta 2.6. Hez. 1.2.\x*; lonina wenkosi, lamakhosikazi enkosi, labathenwa bakhe, lamaqhawe elizwe, yabathumbela eBhabhiloni besuka eJerusalema\x + Eks. 15.15. Hez. 17.13. 32.21.\x*.
\v 16 Lawo wonke amadoda angamaqhawe\x + 24.14. 15.20.\x*, azinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, lezingcitshi zemisebenzi labakhandi, abayinkulungwane, bonke abaqinileyo abangaphuma impi, inkosi yeBhabhiloni yasibaletha bengabathunjwa eBhabhiloni\x + 24.16. Jer. 52.28.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaZedekhiya
\p
\v 17 Inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + Jer. 37.1.\x* yasibeka uMathaniya uyise omncinyane ukuba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 1 Lan. 3.15. 2 Lan. 36.10.\x*, yaguqula ibizo lakhe \add yathi\add* nguZedekhiya\x + 23.34.\x*.
\v 18 UZedekhiya wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanye lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka elitshumi lanye eJerusalema\x + 25.21. Jer. 52.1-27.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguHamutali indodakazi kaJeremiya weLibhina\x + 23.31.\x*.
\v 19 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwenza konke kukaJehoyakhimi\x + 23.37. 2 Lan. 36.12.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba ngenxa yentukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* lokhu kwenzeka eJerusalema lakoJuda yaze yabaxotsha phambi kwayo. UZedekhiya waseyivukela inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 2 Lan. 36.13. Jer. 27.11. Hez. 17.15. Jer. 37.7,8.\x*.